    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chests or tables of various designs used in kitchens or bakeries, having storage areas and a working surface. Used for the storage of flour, making of bread on the table top, and often for the storage of bread. For smaller, counter-top containers used to store bread, use "bread boxes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
